Package edu.aau.g404.api

package edu.aau.g404.api
Provides classes and interfaces for interacting with various smart device APIs.

This package contains classes and interfaces to communicate with different smart device APIs, such as Philips Hue, WiZ, etc. It includes Deserializer interface, LightController, and other general-purpose components for API interaction.
